but not a whole segment.

1369
01:35:54,083 --> 01:35:56,752
Gene, it's gonna work.
   It's gonna work.

1370
01:35:56,886 --> 01:35:59,421
-We're gonna
       go with it.
-[Arthur and Murray laugh]

1371
01:35:59,554 --> 01:36:00,889
Thank you, Murray.

1372
01:36:01,023 --> 01:36:02,191
Couple rules, though.

1373
01:36:02,324 --> 01:36:04,059
No cursing.
No off-color material.

1374
01:36:04,192 --> 01:36:05,761
We do a clean show.

1375
01:36:05,894 --> 01:36:07,062
-Okay?
-Mmm-hmm.

1376
01:36:07,196 --> 01:36:08,697
You'll go on
right after Dr. Sally.

1377
01:36:08,830 --> 01:36:09,832
I love Dr. Sally.

1378
01:36:09,965 --> 01:36:11,267
Good, good.
Someone will

1379
01:36:11,400 --> 01:36:13,635
-come and
get you, okay?
-Okay. Perfect.

1380
01:36:13,769 --> 01:36:14,803
Good luck.

1381
01:36:14,937 --> 01:36:16,137
-Thanks, Murray.
     -Okay.

1382
01:36:17,139 --> 01:36:20,275
-Murray, one small thing.
         -Yeah.

1383
01:36:20,409 --> 01:36:22,144
When you
bring me out,

1384
01:36:22,277 --> 01:36:24,179
