could use a doctor.

1401
01:37:14,463 --> 01:37:15,664
-[audience laughing]
  -[Dr. Sally] Oh!

1402
01:37:15,798 --> 01:37:17,433
Does he have
sexual problems?

1403
01:37:17,567 --> 01:37:19,634
[Murray] Oh, he looks
    like he's got
 a lot of problems.

1404
01:37:19,768 --> 01:37:21,370
[audience laughing]

1405
01:37:21,504 --> 01:37:23,639
All right, Bobby,
let's show that clip
   one last time.

1406
01:37:23,772 --> 01:37:25,473
[Arthur laughing
   on video]

1407
01:37:29,712 --> 01:37:33,014
[Arthur]
<i><font color="white"> I hated school
</font></i><i><font color="white"> as a kid.</font></i>

1408
01:37:34,450 --> 01:37:37,486
<i><font color="white"> But my mother
 would always say,</font></i>

1409
01:37:37,620 --> 01:37:39,388
