1410
01:37:39,522 --> 01:37:42,191
<i><font color="white"> One day,
</font></i><i><font color="white"> you'll have to
 work for a living."</font></i>

1411
01:37:42,324 --> 01:37:43,459
[normal voice]
<i><font color="white"> "No, I won't, Ma.</font></i>

1412
01:37:43,592 --> 01:37:45,627
<i><font color="white"> I'm gonna be
 a comedian."</font></i>

1413
01:37:45,761 --> 01:37:47,628
[Arthur laughing on video]

1414
01:37:51,734 --> 01:37:55,404
-[Murray] Okay.
     You may...
-[audience laughing]

1415
