1431
01:39:15,517 --> 01:39:18,486
This is exactly
how I imagined it.

1432
01:39:20,255 --> 01:39:22,023
Well, that makes
   one of us.

1433
01:39:22,157 --> 01:39:23,625
[audience laughing]

1434
01:39:23,759 --> 01:39:24,759
[audience applauding]

1435
