   this look is not
a political statement.

1438
01:39:34,903 --> 01:39:36,171
Is that right?

1439
01:39:36,305 --> 01:39:37,573
That's right, Murray.
 I'm not political.

1440
01:39:37,706 --> 01:39:40,342
I'm just trying to
make people laugh.

1441
