 like trash?

1561
01:45:04,199 --> 01:45:05,634
Call the police, Gene!

1562
01:45:05,767 --> 01:45:06,835
-I'll tell you
  what you get!
-Call the police.

1563
01:45:06,968 --> 01:45:08,636
You get
    what you
fucking deserve!

1564
01:45:09,370 --> 01:45:11,539
[audience screaming]

1565
01:45:27,088 --> 01:45:28,789
[laughing]

1566
