[reporter 1]
<i><font color="white"> ...many wearing
</font></i><i><font color="white"> clown masks.</font></i>

1585
01:46:24,412 --> 01:46:26,048
[overlapping chatter
     continues]

1586
01:46:26,181 --> 01:46:28,117
[Arthur]<i><font color="white"> If it was
</font></i><i><font color="white"> me dying
 on the sidewalk,</font></i>

1587
01:46:28,250 --> 01:46:29,818
<i><font color="white"> -you'd walk
</font></i><i><font color="white"> right over me.
</font></i>-[news anchor 2]<i><font color="white"> To all of</font></i>

1588
01:46:29,952 --> 01:46:31,553
<i><font color="white"> those who have been
 ignored by the system.</font></i>

1589
01:46:31,687 --> 01:46:33,188
[Arthur]<i><font color="white"> And always remember,
</font></i><i><font color="white"> that's life!</font></i>

